\ logistic     The Logistic function and its first derivative
\     logistic =   Exp( c + a x ) / (1 + Exp( c + a x ) )
\   d_logistic = a Exp( c + a x ) / (1 + Exp( c + a x ) )^2

\ Forth Scientific Library Algorithm #4

